STEP 3 — QUARTERLY P-VALUES  |  Data: PAST 1 YEAR  (display only)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

These results are FOR DISPLAY ONLY and do NOT affect the overall pass/fail verdict.

Fresh OLS is computed per quarter (~63 trading days each, Q1 = oldest, Q4 = most recent).
Both directions are shown per quarter, each with its own independently estimated α and β.

Each quarter card shows:
  - Date range
  - ★ Lower p-value direction: "TICKER_Y (Y) on TICKER_X (X)  β=X.XXX" + p-value
  -   Other direction: "TICKER_Y (Y) on TICKER_X (X)  β=X.XXX" + p-value
  - Cointegrated ✓ or Not cointegrated ✗ (based on ★ direction p < 0.05)

Below cards: "X/4 quarters showed cointegration (reference only)."


