STEP 4 — OVERALL VERDICT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

PASS iff:
  • 5yr primary EG p-value < 0.05   AND
  • 2yr primary EG p-value < 0.05

Quarterly (1yr) results do NOT determine the verdict.

Display two-column: 5yr result (✓/✗ + p) | 2yr result (✓/✗ + p)
Final PASS/FAIL banner. Quarterly reference count as footnote.


